    // The maximum possible sum is always a_{n-1} + a_n.
    //
    // Let's consider the four extreme values:
    // A = a_1 + a_2
    // B = a_{n-1} + a_n
    // C = a_1 + a_2 + h
    // D = a_{n-1} + a_n + h
    //
    // The actual min_f will be one of A or C.
    // The actual max_f will be one of B or D.
